description: Wes was the first Marine I spotted and sicked Big Jake on and the same night he called us back and invited us to his hotel 'party room.' Once at his hotel I gave him the scoop and we whisked him off in our rental car to our hotel room. Wes is 6'1', 185 lbs. and rock solid like any well-trained Marine. He's a sweet guy under all that big manliness and loves showing off for the camera. Get to know more about Wes in this session as he introduces himself to us.(Scene 1 of 5 in 'Devil Dawg Dick.')
title: Wes
